CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1957, pg. A12, reads: "STUNNING...FABULOUS...FASCINATING were just some of the adjectives used in connection with the annual Fashion Show given at Schenley High School by the Beauty Shop Owners and Beauticians.... "
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three men wearing light colored dresses and fur stoles, standing on terrazzo floor in Schenley High School for annual Beauty Shop Owners fashion show
